accessibility.text: Our problem - background
Our development team consist of 4 people
We have two sub-teams:
„front-end” team and „back-end” team
Did not know each other before project
Very strong characters - always enforce their opinion
In case of any problems, always ask a lot of questions
Always talk a lot about what they did, what they do and what they going to do
Very active on JIRA - close some tasks, take care about JIRA, create a lot of sub-tasks to show what they do

Know each other since first year, all group projects done together
Very calm and quiet during the meetings
Almost never ask a questions
Not very active on JIRA - sometimes they take a task, open and at the end of sprint just close this task - no sub-tasks, no updates
But… when technical architect offer them his help they always work hard and very effective with him
